Seccomp Profile		No securityContext.seccompProfile or pod-level seccompProfile configured	Violates both Baseline and Restricted policies. Pod runs with Unconfined seccomp profile, allowing containers to execute all syscalls including dangerous syscalls such as ptrace, mount, reboot, significantly increasing attack surface at kernel level
